title: Ministry of Sound Clubbers Guide To Spring 2014
description:
Album Name: Ministry of Sound Clubbers Guide To Spring 2014 (Mixed By the Only & Komes)

Composers/Mixers: 'The Only' and 'KOMES'

Release Date: Not Yet Released - Expected September 12 2014, (6 Days)

File type: Mp3

Bitrate: 256kbps (Reason for non-320kbps given below) 

Genre: Dance

Files: 44 songs (46 originally with 2 absent from the album)

Size: 340mb, roughly 7.23mb/song

Link to iTunes Album: https://itunes.apple.com/au/album/ministry-sound-clubbers-guide/id909257801


Notes: Attempted to make a complete album before the album was officially released. Therefore, I downloaded all songs as videos from YouTube in HD and converted them, however YT only supports Audio bitrate up to 256kbps, even if you upload in tru-320kbps, so this is the reason for the Standard bitrate. I also tried to get it in the same naming format as iTunes uses, however I have not included track numbers. Also I would include Artist - Album however I have no idea how to do this from .mp3 files to a text list, so I have just included the song names list below.
